Package: protonforge
Version: @VERSION@
Section: games
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libqt6core6 (>= 6.0.0), libqt6gui6 (>= 6.0.0), libqt6widgets6 (>= 6.0.0), libqt6network6 (>= 6.0.0), libc6 (>= 2.34)
Maintainer: ProtonForge <noreply@protonforge.dev>
Description: DLSS & Proton Manager for Steam Games
 ProtonForge is a Qt6 application for managing NVIDIA DLSS settings
 and Proton versions for Steam games on Linux.
 .
 Features:
  - Configure DLSS Super Resolution, Ray Reconstruction, and Frame Generation
  - HDR support configuration for Wayland
  - Direct game launch with custom settings
  - Proton-CachyOS and Proton-GE management
  - Per-game settings persistence
  - Frame rate limiting for smooth motion
  - Steam CDN game artwork integration
Homepage: https://github.com/theinvisible/proton-forge
